### Hotel Room Management System - API Test File
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1

### 1. Get all room types
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get active room types
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types/active
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get room type by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Create new room type
POST http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Economy Room",
  "description": "Budget-friendly room with essential amenities",
  "basePrice": 75.00,
  "maxOccupancy": 2,
  "sizeSqm": 20,
  "amenities": "[\"Air Conditioning\", \"TV\", \"WiFi\"]",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/economy-room.jpg"
}

###

### 5. Update room type
PUT http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Standard Room Plus",
  "description": "Enhanced standard room with additional amenities",
  "basePrice": 120.00,
  "maxOccupancy": 2,
  "sizeSqm": 28
}

###

### 6. Search room types
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types/search?q=deluxe
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Get room types by price range
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types/price-range?minPrice=100&maxPrice=200
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Get all rooms
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Get available rooms
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/available
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Get room by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Get room by number
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/number/201
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. Create new room
POST http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "601",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "floor": 6,
  "viewType": "Mountain view",
  "hasBalcony": false,
  "wifiPassword": "hotel601",
  "notes": "Newly renovated room"
}

###

### 13. Update room status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "MAINTENANCE",
  "notes": "Scheduled maintenance for bathroom fixtures"
}

###

### 14. Search rooms with filters
POST http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "AVAILABLE",
  "floor": 2,
  "hasBalcony": true,
  "minPrice": 100,
  "maxPrice": 300
}

###

### 15. Get rooms by status
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/status/AVAILABLE
Accept: application/json

###

### 16. Get rooms by floor
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/floor/2
Accept: application/json

###

### 17. Get room statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/statistics
Accept: application/json

###

### 18. Get rooms needing maintenance
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/maintenance-needed
Accept: application/json

###

### 19. Toggle room type status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/room-types/1/toggle-status
Accept: application/json

###

### 20. Toggle room status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/hotel-management/api/v1/rooms/1/toggle-status
Accept: application/json

###